<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">
<head>
<meta charset="UTF-8">
<meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
<title>Honeyblade — A.M. Marklund</title>
<link rel="preconnect" href="https://fonts.googleapis.com">
<link rel="preconnect" href="https://fonts.gstatic.com" crossorigin>
<link href="https://fonts.googleapis.com/css2?family=Cormorant+Garamond:ital,wght@0,400;0,500;0,600;1,500&family=EB+Garamond:ital,wght@0,400;0,500;1,400&family=Caveat:wght@500;600&display=swap" rel="stylesheet">
<style>
  :root{
    --navy: #1b2030;
    --navy-light: #262d42;
    --terracotta-1: #d97a3f;
    --terracotta-2: #a8461f;
    --burgundy: #7c1f2c;
    --cream: #f4ede2;
    --cream-dim: #f4ede2cc;
    --ink: #1a1610;
    --gold: #c9a15a;
    --line: rgba(244,237,226,0.18);
  }

  *{ margin:0; padding:0; box-sizing:border-box; }

  body{
    background: var(--cream);
    color: var(--ink);
    font-family: 'EB Garamond', serif;
    -webkit-font-smoothing: antialiased;
  }

  a{ color:inherit; text-decoration:none; }

  /* ---------- NAV (same as homepage) ---------- */
  header.nav{
    background: var(--navy);
    color: var(--cream);
    display:flex;
    align-items:center;
    justify-content:space-between;
    padding: 22px 5vw;
    position: relative;
    z-index: 10;
  }

  .brand{
    display:flex;
    align-items:center;
    gap:12px;
    font-family:'Cormorant Garamond', serif;
    font-size: 1.05rem;
    letter-spacing: 0.28em;
    text-transform: uppercase;
  }

  .brand svg{ width:34px; height:34px; flex-shrink:0; }

  nav.links{
    display:flex;
    gap: 38px;
    font-size: 0.95rem;
    letter-spacing: 0.12em;
    text-transform: uppercase;
    font-family: 'EB Garamond', serif;
  }

  nav.links a{
    opacity: 0.85;
    border-bottom: 1px solid transparent;
    padding-bottom: 4px;
    transition: opacity .2s, border-color .2s;
  }
  nav.links a:hover, nav.links a:focus-visible{
    opacity: 1;
    border-color: var(--gold);
  }
  nav.links a.active{
    border-color: var(--cream);
  }

  /* ---------- SERIES HEADER ---------- */
  section.series-header{
    background: var(--navy);
    padding: 4vw 5vw 1.5vw;
    text-align: center;
  }

  .series-header h1{
    font-family:'Cormorant Garamond', serif;
    font-weight:600;
    color: var(--cream);
    font-size: clamp(2.2rem, 4.6vw, 3.6rem);
    letter-spacing: 0.01em;
  }

  /* ---------- BOOK BLOCK ---------- */
  section.book-block{
    background: var(--navy);
    padding: 2vw 5vw 6vw;
  }

  .book-inner{
    display:grid;
    grid-template-columns: minmax(220px, 340px) minmax(0, 640px);
    gap: 6vw;
    align-items:start;
    max-width: 1200px;
    margin: 0 auto;
  }

  .cover-slot{
    grid-column: 1;
    aspect-ratio: 2/3;
    border: 2px solid rgba(244,237,226,0.25);
    border-radius: 2px;
    overflow: hidden;
    box-shadow: 0 18px 40px rgba(0,0,0,0.45);
  }

  .cover-slot img{
    width: 100%;
    height: 100%;
    object-fit: cover;
    object-position: center;
    display: block;
  }

  .book-copy{
    grid-column: 2;
    padding-top: 0.5rem;
  }

  .book-copy .title{
    font-family:'Cormorant Garamond', serif;
    font-weight:600;
    color: var(--gold);
    font-size: clamp(2.2rem, 4.4vw, 3.2rem);
    line-height: 1.05;
    margin-bottom: 0.4rem;
  }

  .book-label{
    font-size: 0.78rem;
    letter-spacing: 0.18em;
    text-transform: uppercase;
    color: var(--cream);
    margin-bottom: 1.3rem;
  }

  .book-copy .blurb{
    color: var(--cream-dim);
    font-size: 1.02rem;
    line-height: 1.65;
    margin-bottom: 1.5rem;
  }

  .vibes-line{
    color: var(--cream-dim);
    font-size: 1rem;
    line-height: 2;
    margin-bottom: 1.5rem;
  }

  .tagline{
    font-style: italic;
    color: var(--cream-dim);
    font-size: 0.98rem;
    line-height: 1.6;
    margin-bottom: 1.8rem;
  }

  .cta-row{
    display:flex;
    gap: 16px;
    flex-wrap: wrap;
  }

  .cta{
    padding: 12px 30px;
    font-size: 0.8rem;
    letter-spacing: 0.12em;
    text-transform: uppercase;
    border: 1px solid transparent;
    border-radius: 40px;
    cursor: pointer;
    transition: transform .15s ease, box-shadow .15s ease;
    display:inline-block;
  }
  .cta:hover{ transform: translateY(-1px); }
  .cta-secondary{
    background: var(--navy-light);
    color: var(--cream);
    border: 1px solid var(--line);
  }

  /* ---------- FOOTER (same as homepage) ---------- */
  footer{
    background: var(--navy);
    border-top: 1px solid var(--line);
    padding: 1.6rem 5vw 2.2rem;
    display:flex;
    align-items:center;
    justify-content:space-between;
    flex-wrap: wrap;
    gap: 1.2rem;
    color: var(--cream);
  }
  footer .brand{ font-size: 0.9rem; letter-spacing: 0.08em; }
  footer nav.links{ font-size: 0.82rem; gap: 26px; }

  .footer-brand-block{
    display: flex;
    flex-direction: column;
    gap: 6px;
  }

  .copyright{
    font-size: 0.72rem;
    letter-spacing: 0.02em;
    text-transform: none;
    color: var(--cream-dim);
  }

  @media (max-width: 880px){
    .book-inner{
      grid-template-columns: 1fr;
      text-align:center;
    }
    .cover-slot{
      max-width: 320px;
      margin: 0 auto 2rem;
    }
    .cta-row{
      justify-content:center;
    }
    header.nav{ flex-direction:column; gap: 16px; }
    nav.links{ gap: 18px; flex-wrap: wrap; justify-content:center; }
    footer{ flex-direction:column; text-align:center; }
  }

  @media (max-width: 480px){
    nav.links{ font-size: 0.8rem; gap: 12px 16px; }
  }
</style>
</head>
<body>

<header class="nav">
  <div class="brand">
    <svg viewBox="0 0 48 48" fill="none" xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg">
      <circle cx="24" cy="24" r="22.5" stroke="#f4ede2" stroke-width="1.2"/>
      <text x="24" y="30" text-anchor="middle" font-family="Cormorant Garamond, serif" font-size="20" fill="#f4ede2">AM</text>
    </svg>
    A.M. Marklund
  </div>
  <nav class="links">
    <a href="index.html">Home</a>
    <a href="honeyblade.html" class="active">Books</a>
    <a href="https://www.amazon.com/stores/author/B0H2F5CYK8/allbooks" target="_blank">Store</a>
    <a href="index.html#connect">Stay Connected</a>
    <a href="index.html#about">About</a>
  </nav>
</header>

<section class="series-header">
  <h1>The Honeyblade Duology</h1>
</section>

<section class="book-block">
  <div class="book-inner">

    <div class="cover-slot">
      <img src="images/Honeyblade.jpg" alt="Honeyblade book cover">
    </div>

    <div class="book-copy">
      <h2 class="title">Honeyblade</h2>
      <div class="book-label">Book One</div>

      <p class="blurb">
        <!-- Replace this paragraph with your real back-cover blurb -->
        A stolen name. A crown built on lies. And an enemy she was never supposed to fall for.
        In a court built on secrets, one wrong word could cost her everything — including her heart.
      </p>

      <div class="vibes-line">
        ⚔️ Enemies to lovers<br>
        👑 Court intrigue and false identity<br>
        🍯 Slow burn romance
      </div>

      <p class="tagline">
        <!-- Replace this with your own one-line hook -->
        In this medieval fantasy romance, expect royal courtship trials, political scheming, and a slow burn love that could cost her everything.
      </p>

      <div class="cta-row">
        <a href="https://www.amazon.com/Honeyblade-Duology-Book-1-ebook/dp/B0H2BWSPKY" target="_blank" class="cta cta-secondary">
          Pre-order on Amazon
        </a>
      </div>
    </div>

  </div>
</section>

<footer>
  <div class="footer-brand-block">
    <div class="brand">A.M. Marklund</div>
    <div class="copyright">© 2026 A.M. Marklund. All rights reserved.</div>
  </div>
  <nav class="links">
    <a href="index.html">Home</a>
    <a href="honeyblade.html">Books</a>
    <a href="https://www.amazon.com/stores/author/B0H2F5CYK8/allbooks" target="_blank">Store</a>
    <a href="index.html#connect">Stay Connected</a>
    <a href="index.html#about">About</a>
  </nav>
</footer>

</body>
</html>
